headline: Could Dell's (DELL) New Distribution Deal Illuminate Its Competitive Edge in AI Infrastructure?
summary: Earlier this month, D&H Canada announced a new agreement to distribute Dell Technologies’ endpoint solutions and PowerEdge servers, giving partners access to Dell’s product portfolio and professional services to accelerate business transformation. This collaboration aligns with the broader momentum surrounding Dell’s AI-optimized hardware and expanding enterprise partnerships, underscoring the company’s growing influence in the rapidly evolving AI infrastructure market.
